{"tid":2305404,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有諗過會去大灣區發展？","createTime":"2020-11-29T15:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T17:53:52.000Z","uid":305058,"like":22,"dislike":151,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4efc4f15156a16ad6f26fdab4ad2d38002e64f55","tid":2305404,"uid":305058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:03:44.000Z","msg":"如果冇發生過反送中等等嘅事件<br />\n令大家心態改變 意識到個現實<br />\n以前平時得閒會上下深圳當去旅行<br />\n得閒淘下寶 食海底撈嘅<br />\n究竟有冇諗過北上發展？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前有諗過下 試下又無妨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪玩啦痴線 邊個會想去？？<br />\n<br />\n玩就還可以<br />\n去發展就從來冇諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48cb5f938ec57b4097490d70918bb6113c49e92f","tid":2305404,"uid":283700,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"可以貪幾多又唔講 都唔係有心比我地上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afefa3db3fa2a53edee65a68f898e30559362d29","tid":2305404,"uid":24909,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:10:59.000Z","msg":"應酬搞到胃出血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b82bb1fab4edf4aa3f19634fd2f53ffbbaf9e7b","tid":2305404,"uid":271016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"afefa3db3fa2a53edee65a68f898e30559362d29","tid":2305404,"uid":24909,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:10:59.000Z","msg":"應酬搞到胃出血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"巴打成日上支那做野? <br />\nand做盛行?"},{"pid":"4faed72609de51e488d104f51c4dfa86abf008f1","tid":2305404,"uid":24909,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3b82bb1fab4edf4aa3f19634fd2f53ffbbaf9e7b","tid":2305404,"uid":271016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"afefa3db3fa2a53edee65a68f898e30559362d29","tid":2305404,"uid":24909,"like":3,"dislike":